current_state_duration_secs.description:
Seconds the asset has resided in its CURRENT committed FSM band (engine
`band_since`). Omitted until the engine has stamped it. Read with `state`;
`sustained` is the thresholded view (Spec 03).

released_at.description:
RFC3339 timestamp this version was released. The honest analogue of the
often-requested "adopted_at" — there is no separate adoption column;
release == adoption in this lifecycle (ADR-0003).
